use-case:git

make alias in git 
------------------
git config --global --list ---> to view all alias
git config --global --edit ---> to edit alias
git config --global alias.cls 'status' ---> to create alias
previously --> git status (to view status)
now ---> git cls    (this cmd will give same output as git status provide)
all alias store in --->  vim ~/.gitconfig
C:/Users/kamle/.gitconfig  --->git config file location in your system
